      Melee Attack Executor
      Parameters:
      memory - Used to read the memory of the attack target
      speed - The speed of movement towards the attacking target
      maxSenseRange - The maximum range of attack targets
      clearDataWhenLose - Clear your memory when you lose your target
      coolDown - Attack cooldown (in tick)
      effects - Give the target potion effect
